    <p>
        Personal Information: We may collect personal information, such as your name, email address, phone number, and location, when you voluntarily provide it to us for adoption purposes.
        Non-Personal Information: We may collect non-personal information, such as browser type, IP address, and cookies, to enhance your browsing experience and improve our website.
    </p>
    <h2>Information Usage:</h2>
    <p>
        Adoption Process: We may use your personal information to facilitate the pet adoption process, including contacting you regarding potential matches and arranging meet-and-greet sessions.
        Communication: We may use your contact information to send you updates, newsletters, or important notifications related to pet adoption, events, or fundraising campaigns. 
        You can opt out of receiving such communications at any time.
        Website Improvement: We may analyze non-personal information to improve our website's functionality, content, and user experience.
    </p>
    <h2>Information Sharing:</h2>
    <p>
        Third-Party Service Providers: We may share your personal information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website, conducting adoption processes, or providing other related services. 
        These providers are bound by confidentiality agreements and are only authorized to use the information as necessary to perform their services.
        Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to comply with applicable laws, regulations, or legal processes, or in response to valid governmental requests.
    </p>
    <h2>Contact Us:</h2>
    <p>
        If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or the handling of your information, 
        please contact us at +63 9052800700 or email us at fureverhomes@gmail.com.  
    </p>
    <h2>By using the FurEver Homes website, you signify your acceptance of this Privacy Policy.</h2>
